article.headline: Seldon's 26 help Gardner-Webb beat North Carolina Central 88-82
article.description: — Anthony Seldon had 26 points in Gardner-Webb's 88-82 win against North Carolina Central on Friday.
article.linkText: Seldon's 26 help Gardner-Webb beat North Carolina Central 88-82
article.story: DURHAM, N.C. -- — Anthony Seldon had 26 points in Gardner-Webb's 88-82 win against North Carolina Central on Friday. Seldon added five rebounds for the Runnin' Bulldogs (1-1). Darryl Simmons II scored 18 points and added six rebounds. Ademide Badmus shot 6 of 6 from the field and 2 for 3 from the line to finish with 14 points. Josh Smith led the way for the Eagles (0-2) with 21 points, five assists and three steals. Dionte Johnson added 16 points for North Carolina Central. Po'Boigh King also had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
